request.description:
Returns the Google OAuth 2.0 authorization URL as JSON. This endpoint generates a URL with a CSRF state token that the client should use to redirect the user to Google for authentication. After authorization, Google will redirect to the callback endpoint.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "url": "https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/auth?...",
    "state": "uuid-v4-token"
  }
}
```

